  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/25a58481da79dd86c8ff674ba875f797.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/25a58481da79dd86c8ff674ba875f797.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/25a58481da79dd86c8ff674ba875f797.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/46d0944863545d048aeb5dfd672f19d4.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/46d0944863545d048aeb5dfd672f19d4.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/46d0944863545d048aeb5dfd672f19d4.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1-6 Player Local Multiplayer<br></li><li> Create, throw, catch, and block Rocks<br></li><li> 11 Powerups<br></li><li> 24 Maps</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/df6cef9250c81e4a0f54a219486b47cf.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/df6cef9250c81e4a0f54a219486b47cf.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/df6cef9250c81e4a0f54a219486b47cf.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SIMPLE MECHANICS</strong></h2>It only takes one button to create and throw rocks. But you can also do the usual platform movement with a jump, double jump, and dash. While the rock throwing also gives you a boost and refills your double jump.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/f2bf12251916411540a4537b658d0a00.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/f2bf12251916411540a4537b658d0a00.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/f2bf12251916411540a4537b658d0a00.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COLLECT POWER-UPS</strong></h2>Collect firelights and gain power-ups like spikes, triple rocks, or shotguns. Combine the power-ups to change the balance of the playing field.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/0b2f0146482ef3240e9efd041a9d0094.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/0b2f0146482ef3240e9efd041a9d0094.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/0b2f0146482ef3240e9efd041a9d0094.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER YOUR BENDING MOVEMENT</strong></h2>Once the game clicks with you, moving through the levels and taking your shots becomes intuitive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/45f2be090b1243698237930fc3b5f84c.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/45f2be090b1243698237930fc3b5f84c.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/45f2be090b1243698237930fc3b5f84c.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>24 LEVELS</strong></h2>The game features maps with two distinct art styles and minimalist arena maps.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/87b47ed3d77784a5b49233450dc3e84a.avif?t=1720869244\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras_big/87b47ed3d77784a5b49233450dc3e84a.avif?t=1720869244 width=800 height=450 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/46d0944863545d048aeb5dfd672f19d4.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/46d0944863545d048aeb5dfd672f19d4.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/46d0944863545d048aeb5dfd672f19d4.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1-6 Player Local Multiplayer<br></li><li> Create, throw, catch, and block Rocks<br></li><li> 11 Powerups<br></li><li> 24 Maps</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/df6cef9250c81e4a0f54a219486b47cf.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/df6cef9250c81e4a0f54a219486b47cf.webm?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/df6cef9250c81e4a0f54a219486b47cf.mp4?t=1720869244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SIMPLE MECHANICS</strong></h2>It only takes one button to create and throw rocks. But you can also do the usual platform movement with a jump, double jump, and dash. While the rock throwing also gives you a boost and refills your double jump.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224760/extras/f2bf12251916411540a4537b658d0a00.poster.avif?t=1720869244\" width=616 height=20